      <description><![CDATA[两名埃及安全消息人士周一告诉路透社，哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战联盟拒绝了埃及提出的放弃加沙地带权力以换取永久停火的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-islamic-jihad-reject-giving-up-power-return-permanent-ceasefire-egyptian-2023-12-25/</guid>
