    <item>
      <title>教宗在圣诞节致辞中谴责加沙平民死亡“令人震惊”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/christmas-day-message-pope-decries-gazas-appalling-harvest-civilian-deaths-2023-12-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[教皇方济各称在包括加沙在内的战争中死去的儿童为“今天的小耶稣”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/christmas-day-message-pope-decries-gazas-appalling-harvest-civilian-deaths-2023-12-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 11:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
